headline: Arthur J. Gallagher purchases Hann Insurance Brokers and Caytons Law
summary: Hann Insurance Brokers offers property and casualty (P&C) insurance services for commercial clients across Australia, specialising in transport.

headline: Arthur J. Gallagher & Co. Acquires Dawson & Keenan Insurance Ltd
summary: Arthur J. Gallagher & Co. today announced the acquisition of Sault Ste. Marie, Ontario-based Dawson & Keenan Insurance Ltd. Terms of the transaction were not disclosed.
